{"tid":881640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 金巴司機直踩13小時 幾乎沒有時間食飯和上廁所，「扒兩口就要開車」","createTime":"2018-10-29T15:06:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T01:57:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f5c476e4c63d4f832c73b49703f4c6b5792c1575","tid":881640,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T15:06:49.000Z","msg":"《香港01》接觸到其中一位駕駛港澳線的金巴司機，他表示昨日工作近13小時，駕駛金巴穿梭大橋12程，即來回大橋六次，「公司要求我們行十轉，但昨日行了12轉，超出人體極限，好多司機已經開到渾渾噩噩、好容易瞌眼瞓。」<br />\n<br />\n他指港珠澳大橋風大，開車更加不穩定，加上一條直路，巴士設有限速，令司機很容易瞌眼瞓。昨日金巴大排長龍，他說<span style=\"color: red;\">很多司機幾乎沒有時間食飯和上廁所，「扒兩口就要開車」。</span><br />\n<br />\n目前港珠澳大橋港澳線，有約四五十名司機，每日輪三更，每更12個小時，加上到港珠澳大橋香港口岸上下班需要三小時，每日工作時間近16小時，公司更預告大橋開通首半個月不能放假，「你覺得危不危險？」<br />\n<br />\n司機由冠忠巴士集團旗下的公司抽調，他亦是其中之一。他形容抽調至駕駛金巴後，收入大減，「金巴每走一程，只有60元，加上底薪，月入約2.3萬元，比駕駛跨境長途巴士2.8至3.2萬元低很多。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/252668/%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B-%E7%A9%BF%E6%A2%AD%E9%87%91%E5%B7%B4%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E7%9B%B4%E8%B8%A913%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82-%E8%B6%85%E4%BA%BA%E9%AB%94%E6%A5%B5%E9%99%90-%E5%A5%BD%E6%98%93%E7%9E%8C%E7%9C%BC%E7%9E%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F252668%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258F%25A0%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A9%258B-%25E7%25A9%25BF%25E6%25A2%25AD%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%259B%25B4%25E8%25B8%25A913%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582-%25E8%25B6%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%25AB%2594%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E9%2599%2590-%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E6%2598%2593%25E7%259E%258C%25E7%259C%25BC%25E7%259E%2593&d=9OaXB6WGjD8vp30%2BIkAOBsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=9bf3239c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/252668/%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B-%E7%A9%BF%E6%A2%AD%E9%87%91%E5%B7%B4%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E7%9B%B4%E8%B8%A913%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82-%E8%B6%85%E4%BA%BA%E9%AB%94%E6%A5%B5%E9%99%90-%E5%A5%BD%E6%98%93%E7%9E%8C%E7%9C%BC%E7%9E%93</a>"},{"pid":"8268eff4779952f35f0f4a98522f3eb42c594a81","tid":881640,"uid":25858,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T15:09:49.000Z","msg":"罷工啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd17c5c0b56218397d0037b64831d485136bc5cf","tid":881640,"uid":85659,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T15:12:21.000Z","msg":"Lm睇成車鏟落海<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eea4b0c61ef4c67b4ed6f125f750b0220812765","tid":881640,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T15:14:10.000Z","msg":"咁咪好囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持撞橋"},{"pid":"4f8cb28235c110d2adb646288d0942cc94117177","tid":881640,"uid":79410,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T15:19:08.000Z","msg":"冠忠不嬲西架啦<br />\n2.3萬不如楂九巴城巴好過."},{"pid":"34e3bd0d8292c8969c44caea963650adf7aacd61","tid":881640,"uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T15:21:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tfTpS96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtfTpS96.jpg&h=5a27afbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yhb66u7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhb66u7.jpg&h=dc74d47f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c75PjP7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc75PjP7.jpg&h=10a3e6c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"305177ca373666391f88e4d6d9bbcba0b60c14dd","tid":881640,"uid":34742,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T15:21:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f4a5393c935f04dc6fcea01270cba4c07d5b5f0","tid":881640,"uid":67771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T15:23:06.000Z","msg":"港澳線都跨境，點解比跨境長途巴士少成萬蚊"},{"pid":"81